WEBVTT

00:00:00.150 --> 00:00:09.020
What happens after you hit Send. Here's a quick preview of the IntakeBrief process, shown with sample data.

00:00:12.150 --> 00:00:23.060
Your inquiry goes straight to the firm's inbox. Real email, with your topic identified. No dashboard for staff to check.

00:00:24.150 --> 00:00:32.710
You get a real reply in seconds. Specific to your topic, not a generic “we received your message” note.

00:00:36.150 --> 00:00:45.860
Pick a consultation time. Real availability, shown in your time zone, held for fifteen minutes while you decide.

00:00:48.150 --> 00:00:57.290
A fifty dollar deposit reserves your slot. Secure checkout. The firm never sees your card details.

00:01:00.150 --> 00:01:09.360
Confirmation by email. Your time is confirmed only after payment is verified. No surprises.
